# Normalize line endings. Source/text files use LF in the repo; Git converts to
# the host's native ending on checkout per core.autocrlf.
* text=auto

# Shell scripts MUST stay LF — they run on the Jetson (Linux). CRLF breaks the
# shebang / `set -e` parsing.
*.sh text eol=lf

# Windows-only scripts stay CRLF.
*.ps1 text eol=crlf

# Treat model artifacts / binaries as binary (defense-in-depth; also gitignored).
*.engine binary
*.onnx binary
